high_descs: Turn around, walk towards the stove, turn left to face the stove.
Pick up the water kettle from the stove.
Turn left and walk towards the sink.
Turn on the faucet to clean the kettle.
Turn around, walk towards the wall, and then make a right to face the wooden shelf.
Place the kettle on the second to bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Clean the kettle to place it on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn to the right and move towards the brown shelves then turn to the right and move to the oven and the turn to the left to face the oven.
Pick up the tea kettle from the top of the oven.
Turn right and move to the sink.
Place the tea kettle in the center of the sink, turn on the water, turn off the water, and then pick up the tea kettle from the sink.
Turn left and move towards the brown shelves and then turn right to face the shelves.
Place the tea kettle on the right side of the second shelf from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean tea kettle on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn right and walk until you clear the island to your right and when you do turn right and walk until you're even with the stove and when you are turn left and walk to it.
Pick up the teapot that's in front of you.
Turn right and take a step to your right then walk to the sink.
Wash the teapot in the sink then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and walk until you're almost to the wall then turn right to face the shelves.
Put the teapot to the right of the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a teapot on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the stove top.
Pick up the kettle from the stove top.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the kettle in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room to the shelves near the wall on the right.
Put the kettle on the right side of the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned kettle on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn around, hang left, and walk to the stove.
Pick up the kettle on the stove.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the kettle in the sink.
Turn around and walk forward to the end of counter, where there's a set of drawers.
Put the kettle on the second to the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed kettle on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the stove.
Pick up the teapot off of the stove.
Turn right, walk to the sink.
Wash the teapot in the sink.
Turn around, cross the room, turn right to face the shelves.
Put the teapot on the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place the clean teapot on the second shelf.
